New, revolutionary, patented WristWrap® integrates the entire hand for maximum stability and support. The graduated, patented WristWrap® insures proper positioning of the hand and wrist helping to prevent hyperextension. "No-Slip" "Dura-Grip™" rubber pads on the palm and fingers grab the bar providing increased traction, cushioning and durability. Innovative curved finger design fits the natural shape of the hand. Exclusive machine wash & air dry "Comfort Tech" leathers and fabrics stay supple, comfortable and last longer. NoSweat™ materials wick moisture away for increased comfort.
